{"tid":1870822,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同男朋友上床，但係未搞 佢就嬲左我","createTime":"2020-02-09T05:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T04:31:49.000Z","uid":35361,"like":7,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"63967a9d7b2e92db5707e4c7903cc99ff90517cc","tid":1870822,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"早幾日去左男朋友屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢屋企冇人, 緊係要大戰連場啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家好快手就除哂衫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你又摷下我, 我又咀下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大家都摷到high哂, 佢又扯到恆哂 準備埋牙之制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁佢諗住入我先, 但我當時話 : 我依家都硬哂喎, 次次都係你入先, 不如今次我入你先 比我出一獲先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢即時黑面話我唔理佢感受, 只顧自己出野 果晚大家不歡而散 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實大家都扯到硬哂, 邊個入先會好D?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daaaaed14e3fb58b7af24473b871c58bf5c2e2e8","tid":1870822,"uid":25771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"19f2dd6275ef5a893c98006b83c1ed62ff5e3899","tid":1870822,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"格劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48401bb07d0dcf44cbdb1